  <summary date="2019-12-12T22:40:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Stopping Grinch Bots Act of 2019

This bill makes it unlawful to use automated tools (i.e., bots) to intentionally bypass a website's security measures in order to purchase and resell its products or services in interstate commerce.</summary>
